We are proud to announce that Gabriel Picolo is now represented by Chiaroscuro Studios for art sales!

Gabriel Picolo is a brazilian comic artist and illustrator, mostly known worldwide due to his Teen Titans fanarts, which have yielded him the opportunity to work for DC on a series of Graphic Novels. He has also worked for clients worldwide as an illustrator and comic artist.

Picolo works exclusively on digital and his published art pieces on best selling graphic novels will be available for purchase as collectible single-copy Artistâ€™s Proofs, which include a hand-drawn character pencilled by Picolo. Thatâ€™s your chance to own a truly unique, signed art piece by your favorite artist!

The first art drop will be available on Saturday, January 20th. Stay tuned!
